nme.com/news/music/newjeans-super-shy-3464950">《Super Shy》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jung-ho-yeon-tony-leung-newjeans-cool-with-you-music-video-3470889">《Cool With You》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-mini-album-get-up-release-date-teasers-3457710">《ETA》</a>三首主打歌为主导，并伴随发布了六首不同的音乐视频。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-get-up-asap-music-video-release-3473520">B面歌曲《ASAP》的视觉图</a>今天在午夜KST公开。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-iu-palette-celebrity-hurt-cover-performance-3473566">聆听 NewJeans 对 IU 的《Celebrity》的温馨翻唱，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
